# Root workspace — copy to `.env` only if you use env vars at the monorepo root.
# Frontend secrets usually live in Next env files; backend uses `backend/.env`.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Lock files policy (dependency manifests are gitignored)
# Ignored: package-lock.json (root + backend), pnpm-lock.yaml, yarn.lock
# After clone run: npm install (repo root), npm install (backend/), etc.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
